623
00:33:49,961 --> 00:33:51,695
Right. So I've heard. Mm-hmm.

624
00:33:52,964 --> 00:33:55,966
Hey, listen, are you, um, are you hungry?

625
00:33:55,968 --> 00:33:57,434
Can I buy you lunch?

