643
00:35:00,532 --> 00:35:02,065
Customers got a real kick out of me.

644
00:35:02,067 --> 00:35:05,202
- I bet.
- Mm-hmm.

645
00:35:05,204 --> 00:35:08,538
So, is that why you moved here
with Katie after the...

