1452
01:27:48,697 --> 01:27:51,198
Now tell me why I shouldn't have
your firm dismantled

1453
01:27:51,200 --> 01:27:52,566
and sold for scrap this very instant.

1454
01:27:52,568 --> 01:27:54,201
